Credits: Delta, Creator of Iskape, Modelers, Tutorial makers, Me[/size] [size=12pt]Content added by me Npc Points! Slayer Points Pking Points shops for each, max level 150, Custom training areas, Custom barrows Kalphite, tunnels and queen Portals to get around All skills working to a greater or lesser degree Clickable skilltab to train Tons of custom bosses Tons of normal bosses! custom Dungeoneering Tons of dungeoneering armour and Weapons Tons of other custom items Working Double experience ring! Working ring of wealth blood necklace Custom Quest tab 4 slayer masters, each giving different leveled tasks Pvp armours Revenents Strykewyrms Barrelchest Custom Clue Scrolls Custom Challenge scrolls Bronze(g)!!!!!!!!!! Chaotics Ice Queen Updated Tzhaar Area Rocktails and Cavefish Custom Rangers mini Custom monkey mini Custom kamil/Dessous Area Custom Penguin/wolf mini Promethium Primal Celestial Saggatarian Working Overloads Custom home Strykewyrm bones Slayerhelm Keris And Tons More!
Edit:Chooseable Exp Rates! [/size]
Bugs, fixes Two big things come to mind, when creating a new account the game nulls out and creats a blank character file, if omeone fixes and hosts this please ling it to me, idc about credit but i would love to play
Also the wind strike hits 200 xD thats a 5 second fix though, think of that as an anti-leech
